data.description: Nestled Decatur's Emerald Estates this fully renovated 4 bedroom 2.5 bathroom split level with over 2,075 sqft presents a captivating blend of modern sophistication and timeless charm. This fully renovated residence boasts an open and airy floor plan with perfect natural light. The recent updates include a newly designed modern kitchen, featuring stainless steel appliances, pristine white Shaker cabinets, and sleek Quartz countertops, a complete re-plumb , new lighting fixtures and updated electrical , a new roof, fresh interior and exterior paint and new carpet and laminate flooring. With spacious living areas and a full basement, this home offers versatility for all lifestyles. Step onto the back porch and take in the expansive backyard, a perfect setting for outdoor enjoyment. This Spacious home is conveniently close to parks, shopping, and dining! this property offers the perfect balance of comfort and convenience.
